# id: InputSplitAssigner -> InputSplit getNextInputSplit(String host, int taskId)_
commentText: Returns the next input split that shall be consumed. The consumer's host is passed as a parameter_to allow localized assignments.__@param host The host address of split requesting task._@param taskId The id of the split requesting task._@return the next input split to be consumed, or null if no more splits remain.
